\c 15
\s Nhaka yaJudha
\p
\v 1 Mugove worudzi rwavana vaJudha nemhuri dzavo wakasvikira pamuganhu waEdhomu, iko kurenje reZini kurutivi rwechamhembe, kusvikira kuchamhembe kwazvo.
\v 2 Muganhu wavo wekuchamhembe wakabva pamuganhu weGungwa roMunyu, kubva apo pakapinda nyika mugungwa, panotarira kurutivi rwekuchamhembe;
\v 3 ndokupfuura kuchamhembe kwegomo reAkirabhimi, ndokupfuura nokurutivi rweZini, ndokukwira nechekuchamhembe kweKadheshi-Bharinea, ndokupfuura napaHezironi, ndokukwira napaAdhari, ndokudzoka napaKarika;
\v 4 ndokupfuura kusvikira paAzimoni, ndokubuda naparukova rweEgipita; muganhu uyu ndokuguma pagungwa; ndiwo unofanira kuva muganhu wekuchamhembe.
\v 5 Muganhu wokumabvazuva wakatanga paGungwa roMunyu kusvikira pamuganhu waJoridhani. Muganhu worutivi rwekumaodzanyemba wakatanga apo panopinda nyika mugungwa kusvikira pamugumo waJoridhani,
\v 6 ndokukwira kuBheti-hogira, ndokupfuura nokumaodzanyemba kweBheti-arabha; muganhu ndokukwira kubwe raBhohani, mwanakomana waRubheni;
\v 7 muganhu ndokukwira nokuDhebhiri, uchibva pamupata weAkori, ndokudaro uchienda kumaodzanyemba wakatarisana neGirigari, pakatarisanazve negomo reAdhumimi, riri kurutivi rwekuchamhembe kwerwizi; muganhu ndokupfuura napamvura yeEni-shemeshi, ndokuguma paEni-rogeri;
\v 8 muganhu ndokukwira napamupata womwanakomana waHinomi, kusvikira kurutivi rwaVaJebhusi kuchamhembe (ndiro Jerusarema); muganhu ndokukwira kusvikira pamusoro wegomo riri pamberi pomupata weHinomi kumavirazuva, uri pamugumo kwazvo womupata weRefaimu, kurutivi rwekumaodzanyemba.
\v 9 Muganhu ndokumonereka kubva pamusoro pegomo kusvikira kutsime remvura yeNefitoa, ndokuguma pamaguta pagomo reEfuroni; zvino muganhu ndokutarwa kusvikira Bhara (ndiro Kiriati-jearimi).
\v 10 Muganhu ndokudzoka uchibva paBhara nokumavirazuva kusvikira pagomo reSeiri, ndokupfuura nokurutivi rwegomo reJearimi nechekumaodzanyemba (ndiro Kesaroni), ndokuburukira kusvikira paBheti-shemeshi, ndokupfuura napaTimuna;
\v 11 muganhu ndokupfuura kurutivi rweEkironi, kumaodzanyemba; muganhu ndokumonereka kusvikira paShikeroni, ndokupfuura napagomo reBhara, ndokupfuura paJabhuneeri; muganhu ndokuguma pagungwa.
\v 12 Muganhu wokumavirazuva wakasvika kugungwa guru nemuganhu waro. Ndiwo muganhu wavana vaJudha kunhivi dzese nemhuri dzavo.
\p
\v 13 Asi wakapa Karebhu mwanakomana waJefune mugove pakati pavana vaJudha; sezvakarairwa Joshua naJehovha, akamupa Kiriyati-Aribha; Abha wakange ari baba vaAnaki (ndiro Hebhuroni).
\v 14 Karebhu akadzingapo vanakomana vatatu vaAnaki, vaiti: Sheshai, naAhimani, naTamai, vanakomana vaAnaki.
\v 15 Akabvapo, akanorwa navaigara Dhebhiri; zita reDhebhiri kare raiva Kiriati-seferi.
\p
\v 16 Karebhu akati: Munhu unorwa neKiriati-seferi, akarikunda, ndichamupa mukunda wangu Akisa, ave mukadzi wake.
\v 17 Ipapo Otinieri, mwanakomana waKenazi, munin'ina waKarebhu, akarikunda; iye akamupa mukunda wake Akisa, akava mukadzi wake.
\v 18 Zvino iye wakati achisvika kwaari, akamukurudzira kuti akumbire munda kuna baba vake; zvino iye akaburuka pambongoro yake, Karebhu akati kwaari: Unoreveiko?
\v 19 Akati: Ndipei chipo; zvamakandiisa kunyika yekuchamhembe, ndipeiwo matsime emvura. Akamupa matsime okumusoro namatsime.
\p
\v 20 Ndiyo nhaka yorudzi rwavana vaJudha nemhuri dzavo.
\v 21 Maguta okumudzivo orudzi rwavana vaJudha kumuganhu waEdhomu kuchamhembe akange ari Kabhezeeri, neEdheri, neJaguri;
\v 22 neKina, neDhimona, neAdhadha,
\v 23 neKedheshi, neHazori, neItanani,
\v 24 neZifi, neTeremi, neBheroti;
\v 25 neHazori-hadhata, neKerioti-hezironi (ndiro Hazori);
\v 26 neAmamu, neShema, neMoradha;
\v 27 neHazari-gadha, neHeshimoni, neBheti-pereti,
\v 28 neHazari-shuari, neBheeri-shebha, neBhiziotia;
\v 29 neBhaara, neiyimi, neEzemi;
\v 30 neEritoradhi, neKesiri, neHorima;
\v 31 neZikiragi, neMadhamana, neSanisana;
\v 32 neRebhaoti, neShirimi, neAini, neRimoni; maguta iwayo ese aiva namakumi maviri namapfumbamwe, pamwe chete nemisha yawo.
\p
\v 33 Pabani pakange pane Eshitaori, neZora, neAshina;
\v 34 neZaNowa, neEniganimi, neTapua, neEnami;
\v 35 neJarimuti, neAdhuramu neSoko, neAzeka;
\v 36 neSharaimi, neAdhitaimu, neGedhera, neGedherotaimi; maguta ane gumi namana, pamwe chete nemisha yawo.
\v 37 Zenani, neHadhasha, neMigadhari-gadhi;
\v 38 neDhirani, neMizipe, neJokiteeri;
\v 39 neRakishi, neBhosikati, neEgironi;
\v 40 neKabhoni, neRamani, neKiterishi;
\v 41 neGedheroti, neBheti-dhagoni, neNaama, neMakedha; maguta ane gumi namatanhatu, pamwe chete nemisha yawo.
\v 42 Ribhina, neEteri, neAshani;
\v 43 neIfita, neShina, neNezibhi;
\v 44 neKeira, neAkizibhi, neMaresha; maguta anamapfumbamwe, pamwe chete nemisha yawo.
\v 45 Ekironi, nemisha yaro, nemisha midiki yaro;
\v 46 kubva paEkironi kusvikira pagungwa, maguta ese akange ari parutivi rweAshidhodhi, pamwe chete nemisha yawo.
\v 47 Ashidhodhi, nemisha yaro, nemisha midiki yaro; neGaza, nemisha yaro, nemisha midiki yaro, kusvikira kurukova rweEgipita, napagungwa guru nemuganhu waro.
\p
\v 48 Nokunyika yamakomo: Shamiri, neJatiri, neSoko;
\v 49 neDhana, neKiriatisana (ndiro Dhebhiri);
\v 50 neAnabhi, neEshitemo, neAnimi;
\v 51 neGosheni, neHoroni, neGiro; maguta ane gumi nerimwe, pamwe chete nemisha yawo.
\v 52 Arabhu, neDhuma, neEshani;
\v 53 neJanimi, neBheti-tapua, neAfeka;
\v 54 neHumuta, neKiriyati-Aribha (ndiro Hebhuroni), neZiori; maguta mapfumbamwe, pamwe chete nemisha yawo.
\v 55 Maoni, neKarimeri, neZifi, neJuta;
\v 56 neJezireeri, neJokidheami, neZaNowa;
\v 57 neKaini, neGibhiya, neTimuna; maguta ane gumi, pamwe chete nemisha yawo.
\v 58 Harikuri, neBheti-zuri, neGedhori;
\v 59 neMaarati, neBheti-anoti, neEritekoni; maguta matanhatu, pamwe chete nemisha yawo.
\v 60 Kiriati-bhaari (ndiro Kiriati-jearimi), neRabha; maguta maviri, pamwe chete nemisha yawo.
\p
\v 61 Murenje pakange pane Bheti-abha, neMidhini, neSekaka;
\v 62 neNibhishani, neGuta roMunyu, neEni-gedhi; maguta matanhatu, pamwe chete nemisha yawo.
\p
\v 63 Asi vana vaJudha vakange vasingagoni kudzinga VaJebhusi vakange vagere Jerusarema; asi VaJebhusi vakagara Jerusarema pamwe chete navana vaJudha kusvikira nhasi.